Amendment No. 3 to SB1926
Massey
Signature of Sponsor
AMEND S e n ate Bill No. 1926* House Bill No. 1991
by deleting SECTION 1 and substituting:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 63-5-108(c), is amended by adding
the following as a new subdivision:
(6) Prior to a dentist seeing a new patient, a dental hygienist working under
direct supervision of the dentist, or, prior to a dentist seeing an existing patient, a dental
hygienist working under general supervision of the dentist may:
(A) Complete diagnostic radiographs;
(B) Assess and record existing hard and soft tissue data;
(C) Perform prophylaxis; and
(D) Apply fluoride agents.
